There are six stats on this MUD, three physical; and three mental, which
generally range from 3 to 18, although some races have modifiers which may
raise a stat above 18, or lower it below 3.

The six stats in the game are strength, constitution, and dexterity
(physical), and charisma, intellignece, and wisdom (mental).

See also: strength, constitution, dexterity, charisma, intellignece, wisdom